Types:
2xx -> Succes -> the request was successfully recieving and processed
3xx -> Redirection -> Futher action needs to taken(e.g, redirect)
4xx -> Client Error -> Something went wrong on the server side
5xx -> Server Error -> Something went wrong on server side

In detail:
200->OK->Standard success
201->Created->resource created
204->No Content->After delete request

400->(Bad Request)Invalid request ->Missing field,wrong datatype
401->(Unauthorized)No/Invalid authentication ->login required
403->(Forbidden)Authenricated but no permission->logged in but not allowed
404->(Not Found)Resource doesn't exist